data.description: 5 acres with a pond in the front and tidal creek with a dock in the back. re. This 5 acre lot is absolutely beautiful, quiet and peaceful. It has an arbor with an abundance of blueberries, a large pond with big large mouth bass and a great cookout area for an oyster roast or family gathering. The house has a great floor plan with updated kitchen and bathrooms. Master bedroom and bath are very spacious with an additional 2 br's on the main floor. Ground floor was remodeled in 2018 with new bathrooms and kitchen. This will satisfy your desire for country living but still close enough to all the things you need.
